    "Our selected RAG-LLM model improved the accuracy of DRP identi cation by 22%.",
    "When deployed autonomously, GPT-4 and RAG-LLM showed subpar performance across all metrics of accuracy, precision, recall and F1.",
    "However, when deployed as a co-pilot, the RAG-LLM model is capable of highlighting DRPs that were missed by LLM and RAG-LLM.",
    "This suggests strongly that for complex reasoning clinical tasks such as medication chart review, LLMs alone are not adequate.",
    "A copilot mode can potentially improve model utility and also performance of human alone."
